  "texts": [
    "Since the labels are provided at the patient level, this approach is also known as multiple instance learning (MIL).",
    "The classification head was then discarded and the resampler was plugged into the vision language model.",
    "We froze all layers of HistoGPT except the cross-attention blocks.",
    "Our generative training is based on causal language modeling: Given an input, we mask the next tokens and let the model predict them.",
    "This is done in parallel over all input tokens using an upper triangular causal attention mask."
